1 Caroline Favrot Trube (John); twelve grandchildren; seven great-grandchildren; and a host
2 of beloved nieces and nephews; she will be deeply missed, but the legacy of her loving
3 generosity shall live on in the hearts and minds of those who were privileged to have known
4 and loved her.
5 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
6 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby express heartfelt condolences on the death of Kathleen
7 "Kay" Gibbons Favrot and does hereby extend sincere wishes that her family, friends, and
8 loved ones find comfort in their shared memories of her beautiful life.
